title: Breaking: Six foreign nationals found in remote WA detained by Border Force
description: A group of six foreign nationals are detained by authorities after two of their group were found in WA's remote Kalumburu community by an off-duty police officer.
content:
A group of six foreign nationals have been discovered in the remote Indigenous community of Kalumburu in the state's north, WA Police say.
